    "asOf": "2019-07-30",
    "date": "2020-04-22T19:16:03Z",
    "text": "This bill provides for full Old Age, Survivors, and Disability Insurance (OASDI) benefits, without regard to age,\u00a0for disabled individuals who are widowed. In addition, the bill exempts\u00a0disabled individuals who are widowed\u00a0from certain reductions in OASDI benefits and otherwise revises provisions related to such reductions."
